屏幕并从偶像设置中选择星街一诚。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.3o0wb1buaf4l-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.3o0wb1buaf4l-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.3o0wb1buaf4l-jpg.webp 500w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.3o0wb1buaf4l-147x300.webp 147w" width="500" height="1020" /></a></p><p>星街彩生出现在AR面前！</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.233h4xvgzmy2-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.233h4xvgzmy2-473x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 473px) 100vw, 473px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.233h4xvgzmy2-473x1024.webp 473w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.233h4xvgzmy2-139x300.webp 139w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.233h4xvgzmy2-jpg.webp 500w" width="473" height="1024" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.6dgtp8ewv81i-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.6dgtp8ewv81i-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.6dgtp8ewv81i-jpg.webp 500w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.6dgtp8ewv81i-147x300.webp 147w" width="500" height="1020" /></a></p><p>如果您从订单[歌曲]中选择“请！灰姑娘”，星町将随着德雷斯特的代表歌曲跳舞。非常有价值的景色！</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.wvt7el1qygji-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.wvt7el1qygji-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.wvt7el1qygji-jpg.webp 500w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.wvt7el1qygji-147x300.webp 147w" width="500" height="1020" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.x8kdgq6bg49u-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.x8kdgq6bg49u-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.x8kdgq6bg49u-jpg.webp 500w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.x8kdgq6bg49u-147x300.webp 147w" width="500" height="1020" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.qebvdwwt6qzc-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.qebvdwwt6qzc-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.qebvdwwt6qzc-jpg.webp 500w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.qebvdwwt6qzc-147x300.webp 147w" width="500" height="1020" /></a></p><p>从【姿势】的顺序，你可以得到各种姿势。果然只是偶像，所有的姿势都已经决定了。您可以随时随地设置相机并一起拍照。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.x3e44rteeb0w-jpg.webp" target="_